{"tid":1378464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盡早向外煲大解放軍入港 要求外國制止","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:41:19.000Z","uid":92790,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b012830747b16659b907f328af901871b45691","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"中共向來視維穩高於一切 包括經濟<br />\n因為只有維穩可以保護共產黨既獨裁統治<br />\n佢地既權威係重要過香港所帶黎既經濟利益<br />\n<br />\n而要制止解放軍 只有外國介入先有可能<br />\n如果外國講到明唔接受解放軍入港<br />\n中共堅持 反而可能造成更大動盪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但萬一中共係外國未反應之前，已經放左老解。<br />\n到時米已成炊，外國可以做既野就少左。<br />\n甚或有老解個陣，香港人想對外文宣都未可能。<br />\n<br />\n所以就算我地自己覺得唔會放老解<br />\n都應該向外國宣傳老解論<br />\n向外國政府施壓<br />\n<br />\n多一層保障唔係壞事<br />\n畢竟萬一放老解<br />\n係可以無限期係香港<br />\n做一切野去消滅我地<br />\n拉人，香港教育營，拉返內地，極速起燈柱<br />\n搞好晒，確保無下一round先走都唔係唔得<br />\n<br />\n中共大飢荒都唔驚，邊會驚你焦土。佢剩係驚外國架"},{"pid":"e9c22d3a137b1c99d3d5fabf0d717464e5607b03","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"我唔想上唔到連登ar"},{"pid":"202f1a65d31bf4ad0b20f9664f825ee9b2b4a00a","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"我唔想用tg就比人拉ar"},{"pid":"a6887eef2e39854ee3b918c21c24441a151a7ad5","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d4a798889c03bb6840fb721b563f0552861fdec","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"84ef927ff0e2fe77980c84b2d9ed2fcd2d94c4c2","tid":1378464,"uid":134751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:44:58.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"587bc33f36b4125fa62df7cc9ea797537767311d","tid":1378464,"uid":138609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"仲有要同親戚朋友講解放軍入城<br />\n到時樓股匯實玩完 分分鐘變廢紙<br />\n記得換定美金保平安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f227735dccd743150fcebcfedb6ce5a9222961","tid":1378464,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38941c7909950c8a7b26eced3cdfee047424ae1","tid":1378464,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:03:37.000Z","msg":"先下手為強<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"5f76fbe1b70000a0e6fe326aabec4ccbcda428f8","tid":1378464,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f66cc8350e8c00f794bfbbc8b80120420cf77546","tid":1378464,"uid":107828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a1c3b079fdeb684ed0c969255fb1561ef47a92c","tid":1378464,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7408226e152245414d033da3feb7b78156a68183","tid":1378464,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:18:46.000Z","msg":"係中國唔係內地，唔好借啲二用共產中文"},{"pid":"704ca243eb8a2e0d28a19dc089aa8d17e0f8efd7","tid":1378464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8a6cc6fb3b85d0e72e5b71f1ecf3dd0d98e1ee","tid":1378464,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68be553c09754d18f3239512c894a4a86a03889f","tid":1378464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif